    With a good majority of the elements striking him, between the ice, fire
and lightning Thrash could feel his hover vents cutting off smoke emerging
from one as the giant shark arrowed down from the low altitude he had
attained, depth charges other five discs flying harmlessly past where he had
originally been. While the fire did little to hurt him the ice choked the
vents and the lightning sizzled his circuitry.

    Tumbling down the shark bot crashed into the turf, transforming into
robot mode a few moments after impact...
